│  ## API Endpoints Summary                                                    │
│                                                                              │
│  | Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |                         │
│  |--------|----------|-------------|---------------|                         │
│  | POST | `/auth/register` | Register new user | No |                        │
│  | POST | `/auth/login` | Login and get token | No |                         │
│  | GET | `/users/me` | Get current user profile | Yes |                      │
│  | PUT | `/users/me` | Update current user profile | Yes |                   │
│  | GET | `/users/{user_id}` | Get user by ID | No |                          │
│  | GET | `/users/` | List all users | No |                                   │
│  | POST | `/comics/` | Create new comic | Yes |                              │
│  | GET | `/comics/` | List all comics | No |                                 │
│  | GET | `/comics/my` | List user's comics | Yes |                           │
│  | GET | `/comics/{comic_id}` | Get comic by ID | No |                       │
│  | PUT | `/comics/{comic_id}` | Update comic | Yes (owner) |                 │
│  | DELETE | `/comics/{comic_id}` | Delete comic | Yes (owner) |              │
│  | POST | `/comics/{comic_id}/panels` | Add panel | Yes (owner) |            │
│  | GET | `/comics/{comic_id}/panels` | List panels | No |                    │
│  | GET | `/comics/{comic_id}/panels/{panel_id}` | Get panel | No |           │
│  | PUT | `/comics/{comic_id}/panels/{panel_id}` | Update panel | Yes         │
│  (owner) |                                                                   │
│  | DELETE | `/comics/{comic_id}/panels/{panel_id}` | Delete panel | Yes      │
│  (owner) |                                                                   │
│  | GET | `/health` | Health check | No |                                     │
│  | GET | `/` | Root info | No |                                              │
│  | GET | `/api/info` | API information | No |                                │
│                                                                              │
